msgstr "Slimme kortingsbonnen voor WooCommerce"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:43
msgid ""
"Create coupons to offer discounts and free products to your customers with "
"Smart Coupons for WooCommerce. You can set up BOGO coupons, giveaways, gift "
"cards, store credits, and more with this plugin."
msgstr ""
"Maak kortingsbonnen om kortingen en gratis producten aan uw klanten aan te "
"bieden met Smart Coupons voor WooCommerce. U kunt BOGO-kortingsbonnen, "
"weggeefacties, cadeaubonnen, winkeltegoed en meer instellen met deze plugin."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:51
#: admin/modules/premium-upgrade/views/page-content.php:188
msgid "URL Coupons for WooCommerce"
msgstr "URL-kortingsbonnen voor WooCommerce"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:52
msgid ""
"Generate custom URLs and QR codes for every discount coupon in your "
"WooCommerce store. These unique coupons are easy to share and can even be "
"set to add new products to the cart upon application."
msgstr ""
"Genereer aangepaste URL's en QR-codes voor elke kortingsbon in uw "
"WooCommerce winkel. Deze unieke kortingsbonnen zijn eenvoudig te delen en "
"kunnen zelfs worden ingesteld om nieuwe producten aan de winkelwagen toe te "
"voegen bij toepassing."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:60
msgid "WooCommerce Coupon Generator plugin"
msgstr "WooCommerce kortingsbon generator plugin"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:61
msgid ""
"Generate coupons in bulk on your WooCommerce store. Add them to the store, "
"email them to recipients or export them to a CSV file. Configure advanced "
"coupon restrictions and offer them to select users."
msgstr ""
"Genereer kortingsbonnen in bulk in uw WooCommerce winkel. Voeg ze toe aan de"
" winkel, e-mail ze naar ontvangers of exporteer ze naar een CSV-bestand. "
"Configureer geavanceerde kortingsbonbeperkingen en bied ze aan geselecteerde"
" gebruikers aan."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:70
msgid ""
"Easily generate & print fully customized PDF Invoices, Packing Slips, and "
"Credit Notes for your orders. Automatically send the documents to the "
"recipients by attaching them to the order status emails."
msgstr ""
"Genereer en print eenvoudig volledig aangepaste PDF-facturen, pakbonnen en "
"creditnota's voor uw bestellingen. Stuur de documenten automatisch naar de "
"ontvangers door ze toe te voegen aan de e-mails met de orderstatus."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:78
msgid "WooCommerce Shipping Labels, Dispatch Labels and Delivery Notes"
msgstr "WooCommerce Verzendlabels, Afzendlabels en Afleveringsnotities"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:79
msgid ""
"Automatically generate WooCommerce Shipping Labels, Dispatch Labels, and "
"Delivery Notes with custom settings and layouts. Customize the label sizes "
"and add extra product or order fields as required."
msgstr ""
"Genereer automatisch WooCommerce Verzendlabels, Afzendlabels en "
"Afleveringsnotities met aangepaste instellingen en lay-outs. Pas de "
"labelgroottes aan en voeg extra product- of ordervelden toe zoals vereist."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:87
msgid "WooCommerce Picklists"
msgstr "WooCommerce Picklijsten"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:88
msgid ""
"Customize, generate and print WooCommerce picklists for all orders on your "
"store and automatically attach them to the order status emails. Add product "
"variation data and other fields to the document."
msgstr ""
"Pas WooCommerce picklijsten aan, genereer en print ze voor alle bestellingen"
" in uw winkel en voeg ze automatisch toe aan de e-mails met de orderstatus. "
"Voeg productvariatiegegevens en andere velden toe aan het document."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:96
msgid "WooCommerce Proforma Invoices"
msgstr "WooCommerce Proforma facturen"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:97
msgid ""
"Automate the generation of WooCommerce proforma invoices when new orders are"
" placed and send them to your customers via order emails. Customize the "
"layout and content of the invoice as per your needs."
msgstr ""
"Automatiseer het genereren van WooCommerce proforma facturen wanneer nieuwe "
"bestellingen worden geplaatst en stuur ze naar uw klanten via order-e-mails."
" Pas de lay-out en inhoud van de factuur aan uw behoeften aan."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:105
msgid "WooCommerce Address Labels"
msgstr "WooCommerce Adreslabels"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:106
msgid ""
"Generate address labels for all orders in your store and easily print them "
"in bulk. Customize the label layout and create labels of different types "
"(shipping, billing, return, from address) with ease."
msgstr ""
"Genereer adreslabels voor alle bestellingen in uw winkel en print ze "
"eenvoudig in bulk. Pas de labelindeling aan en creëer eenvoudig labels van "
"verschillende typen (verzending, facturatie, retour, afzenderadres)."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:114
msgid "WebToffee WooCommerce Product Feed & Sync Manager"
msgstr "WebToffee WooCommerce Productfeed & Sync Manager"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:115
msgid ""
"Generate WooCommerce product feeds for Google Merchant Center and Facebook "
"Business Manager. Use the Facebook catalog sync manager to sync WooCommerce "
"products with Facebook and Instagram shops."
msgstr ""
"Genereer WooCommerce productfeeds voor Google Merchant Center en Facebook "
"Business Manager. Gebruik de Facebook catalogus sync manager om WooCommerce "
"producten te synchroniseren met Facebook en Instagram winkels."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:123
msgid "WebToffee Woocommerce Request a Quote"
msgstr "WebToffee Woocommerce Offerte aanvragen"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:124
msgid ""
"Configure a fully optimized WooCommerce quote request set up in your store. "
"Allow customers to request quotes and store managers to respond to them. "
"Hide product prices, set up email alerts, and more."
msgstr ""
"Configureer een volledig geoptimaliseerde WooCommerce offerteaanvraag in uw "
"winkel. Laat klanten offertes aanvragen en winkelmanagers erop reageren. "
"Verberg productprijzen, stel e-mailwaarschuwingen in en meer."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:133
msgid ""
"Boost the visibility of the products by displaying them as ‘Frequently "
"bought together’ items in your store. You may also set up discounts for "
"Frequently Bought Together bundles with this plugin."
msgstr ""
"Vergroot de zichtbaarheid van de producten door ze weer te geven als 'Vaak "
"samen gekocht' items in uw winkel. U kunt met deze plugin ook kortingen "
"instellen voor bundels die vaak samen worden gekocht."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:141
msgid "GDPR Cookie Consent Plugin (CCPA Ready)"
msgstr "GDPR Cookie Consent Plugin (CCPA-klaar)"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:142
msgid ""
"The plugin helps you get compliant with GDPR, CCPA, and other major cookie "
"laws. You can create and manage cookie consent banners, scan website "
"cookies, and generate cookie policies with this plugin."
msgstr ""
"De plugin helpt u te voldoen aan de AVG, CCPA en andere belangrijke "
"cookiewetgeving. U kunt cookie-toestemmingsbanners maken en beheren, "
"websitecookies scannen en cookiebeleidsregels genereren met deze plugin."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:150
msgid "Product Import Export Plugin For WooCommerce"
msgstr "Product Import Export Plugin voor WooCommerce"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:151
msgid ""
"Seamlessly import/export your WooCommerce products including simple, "
"variable, custom products and subscriptions. You may also import and export "
"product images, tags, categories, reviews, and ratings."
msgstr ""
"Importeer/exporteer naadloos uw WooCommerce-producten, inclusief eenvoudige,"
" variabele, aangepaste producten en abonnementen. U kunt ook "
"productafbeeldingen, tags, categorieën, beoordelingen en recensies "
"importeren en exporteren."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:159
msgid "WordPress Users & WooCommerce Customers Import Export"
msgstr "WordPress Gebruikers & WooCommerce Klanten Import Export"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:160
msgid ""
"Easily import and export your WordPress users and WooCommerce customers "
"using the Import Export plugin for WooCommerce. The plugin supports the use "
"of CSV, XML, TSV, XLS, and XLSX file formats."
msgstr ""
"Importeer en exporteer eenvoudig uw WordPress-gebruikers en WooCommerce-"
"klanten met de Import Export-plugin voor WooCommerce. De plugin ondersteunt "
"het gebruik van CSV-, XML-, TSV-, XLS- en XLSX-bestandsformaten."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:168
msgid "Order, Coupon, Subscription Export Import for WooCommerce"
msgstr ""
"Bestelling, kortingsbon, abonnement exporteren importeren voor WooCommerce"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:169
msgid ""
"Export and Import your WooCommerce orders, subscriptions, and discount "
"coupons using a single Import Export plugin. You may customize the export "
"and import files with advanced filters and settings."
msgstr ""
"Exporteer en importeer uw WooCommerce-bestellingen, abonnementen en "
"kortingsbonnen met behulp van een enkele Import Export-plugin. U kunt de "
"export- en importbestanden aanpassen met geavanceerde filters en "
"instellingen."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:177
msgid "Import Export Suite for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Import Export Suite voor WooCommerce"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:178
msgid ""
"An all-in-one plugin to import and export WooCommerce store data. You can "
"import and export products, product reviews, orders, customers, discount "
"coupons, and subscriptions using this single plugin."
msgstr ""
"Een alles-in-één plugin om WooCommerce winkelgegevens te importeren en "
"exporteren. U kunt producten, productbeoordelingen, bestellingen, klanten, "
"kortingsbonnen en abonnementen importeren en exporteren met deze enkele "
"plugin."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:190
msgid "Sequential Order Numbers for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Sequentiële ordernummers voor WooCommerce"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:191
msgid ""
"Number your WooCommerce orders in a custom, sequential & manageable format. "
"The Sequential Order Number plugin lets your orders follow a custom & unique"
" numbering sequence suitable for your business."
msgstr ""
"Nummer uw WooCommerce-bestellingen in een aangepast, sequentieel en "
"beheerbaar formaat. De Sequential Order Number-plugin laat uw bestellingen "
"een aangepaste en unieke nummerreeks volgen die geschikt is voor uw bedrijf."

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:199
msgid ""
"Accessibility Tool Kit: WP Accessibility Plugin for WCAG, Section 508, ADA, "
"EAA Compliance"
msgstr ""
"Toegankelijkheidstoolkit: WP Toegankelijkheid Plugin voor WCAG, Sectie 508, "
"ADA, EAA Compliance"

#: admin/modules/other-solutions/views/other-solutions-content.php:200
msgid ""
"Build an accessible WordPress site that works for everyone. Scan for "
"accessibility issues, get fix recommendations, and ensure WCAG compliance, "
